Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:41.16,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,For this past year, these are the places I have woken up in with hangovers:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:46.58,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes in the cabin on a torpedo boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.87,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But here was my lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.21,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,A cheap hotel room looking over downtown Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:58.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in a year, I'll leave this country for a far off place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,A place that is far removed from the current me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That country...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:15.02,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Rock? Happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.49,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really feel that way here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.78,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the Chinese's fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.00,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.64,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's decorated nicely for the new year here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.06,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Revy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.88,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,All she does is complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.17,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}Tokarev: a gun of Soviet origin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.96,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't like the Tokarev she was given. She was in a bad mood over that yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.67,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a lady's man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.42,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She came with you because she was worried in her own way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.42,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.74,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.28,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.27,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,New York gets it worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.69,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,but it feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:56.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I left that city, it's been a long time that I haven't seen snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.28,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hit on by a few guys already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:05.45,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}gaijin: Japanese word for foreigner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:05.45,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I talk back, they make a funny face and keep calling me a "gaijin".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This country pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the first time we meet face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.29,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.79,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how should I address you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Balalaika is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard everything from Laptev.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:33.43,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been eager to create a base of operations in Tokyo for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.21,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do appreciate your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.48,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys form a team with us, there'll be nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:44.32,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,As you must have heard, the Kanto Peace Council wants to keep foreigners out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:49.18,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Laptev from Russia was thrown out because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:55.46,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd hold out a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.80,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Washimine Group was part of the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only so much one will suffer for obligation's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.81,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've paid a lot of tribute to the Kousa Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.72,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think we've done a lot for the Peace Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:16.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't stay at the bottom of the pile simply out of obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.23,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our interests are mutually beneficial, Mr. Bando.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:26.45,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to expand your influence with our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:30.25,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will light a new fire in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.74,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quick to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.96,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you suppress the Kousa Council with your power, then the Peace Council can do nothing about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.29,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our emblem still has some power behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:44.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're most used to being in a fire, out of all the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are curious about our forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our forces are nothing like those of this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.52,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.15,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. Are you in position?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:03.47,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:04.85,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Translator.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.65,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's switched to Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:07.99,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:22.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,To start things off, we've blown up one of the clubs owned by the Kousa Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Blown up?! You idiot! What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:32.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Intimidation with handguns is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.81,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we at Hotel Moscow show force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:45.19,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We destroy everything that is in our path. That is why we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.33,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.10,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one hell of a firework to start off the Washimine Group's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.89,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Miss Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:59.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\be0\fnDot Matrix\c&H56BBD4&\shad0\clip(150,125,687,255)\move(570,154,200,154)\q2}3rd  at  6pm,  an  explosion  occurred  at  Kabuki  Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:01.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,All those yakuza were paralyzed with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:04.00,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally get to come back, but that was too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.32,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they wouldn't make my country into a war zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:08.74,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She was in a really great mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:12.59,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been a big fight in Roanapur lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:17.44,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type to give up fucking if there's a war to be had.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.04,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:20.94,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're war maniacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:24.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They left a few screws back in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.86,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rock, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a fair up. It's almost the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:33.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a carnival. Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.87,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.62,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any Ferris wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.33,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have those at Japanese fairs, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.07,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.80,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.64,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're living up to the name of Two Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right. Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:02.73,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,As Miss Rebecca, I have no equal with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:04.78,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:09.32,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame I don't have my Cutlass. I could close this shop down in three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:13.61,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is the hardest country in the world to have a gunfight in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:17.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't bribe the cops here like in Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.20,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get thrown in, it's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.31,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembering something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.67,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:30.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you mean "like what"? This is your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.69,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have anyone, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.13,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,family or such?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you were born from a crotch of a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.31,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought snoops weren't well liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.58,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.81,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were thinking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.19,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,From the time when you pulled a gun on me, on that boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.62,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it. This is a place I knew well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.45,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel like I don't know it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.83,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My family doesn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.34,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My older brother turned out well and got a government job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get into college at first and ended up in a company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:13.84,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't expect much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.65,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they really didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:19.68,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But your folks are alive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.67,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,At least contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been arrested yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.14,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.94,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep this up, one day you won't be able to see them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.79,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,From our point of view, you have a normal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.86,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it worthwhile to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:41.24,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this far without stealing or killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.93,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying you should at least go see their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.34,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say I'm really normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hanging around you guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:00.73,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.06,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! One more and I get the high score!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I bet it's weighed down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.27,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.99,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Hey, Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:22.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she took first place, so give me the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.99,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. She can't cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.66,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it doesn't count,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.96,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,since you knocked it over by poking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.21,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:35.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Speak Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.76,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.64,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.02,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Japan! Speak Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Gin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.40,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Customer, 'scuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.78,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of new year's week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.61,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we all just have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:05.18,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lay your aggression aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.75,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.34,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! Let's go! We're being a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.33,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, baby. Are you taking his side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:24.49,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is short, and we'd all just like to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.75,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You had your fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take this opportunity to save face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.55,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm, sweet wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.62,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like sweet wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:49.73,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold and standing around in the cold is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.53,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:54.81,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:58.03,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like fighting, so lets do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.15,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did we end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.91,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's nothing to gain from making a big scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.12,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even in the mood anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.83,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad it calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:18.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm, well. I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.92,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:21.59,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:27.12,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a student, or are you a vendor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.42,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.85,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:36.54,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was a vendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.02,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.28,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ginji was like my father's student.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:45.36,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an argument here, everyone goes to Mr. Gin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's big, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.87,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he realized it, he was the arbitrator of Takamachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.25,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:57.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would come help close shop after my college entrance exam class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.17,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was a little shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.13,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just ultra short-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.80,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad it didn't cause a big scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.68,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.43,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Chinese-American.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.39,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.64,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,she works with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:19.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to translate for a Russian, and she came with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:23.65,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,An international occupation is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.81,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small company and always troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.54,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lot of work and very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.66,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.62,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Missy, you're not a decent woman are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.83,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.75,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the eyes of a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.44,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.74,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink of blood and guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.04,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, if it gets too cold, it won't be good for your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.59,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.07,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.59,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yukio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki as in snowman and O as in sandal straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:30.57,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:36.60,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,that day, I didn't know how powerful darkness was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.43,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,02:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.99,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We assaulted a Kousa Council office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.54,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Result: 12 kills, no fatalities, no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:14:00.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,All men had left the scene by 02:37.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have them prepare Russian tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:06.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't like making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.12,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How about toast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:08.84,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some, Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:11.14,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:14.10,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't skip breakfast, Sergeant. It's not healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.60,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,When did the police force intervene?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.83,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The scene started to be closed off at 03:05.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.28,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They are on a heightened security status.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a member of the Washimine Group transcribe their wireless communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:29.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We must wait for Rock's translation for the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.91,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The reliability of the information could mean life or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.45,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have him translate it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:37.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,As I would expect from Balalaika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.42,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see why Boss Slevenin acknowledges you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose ass do you think I'm wiping, Vasily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:52.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged the face of the organization through the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}I want to wrap up the operation here and get back to Roanapur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.85,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is full of gunpowder. I can't leave it alone for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.39,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in six hours then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get high and mighty, Balalaika!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:06.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the bosses back in Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:12.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. It's hard to remember those who rose up through money instead of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:15.34,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I better write your name down on a dollar bill so I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.85,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep barking, you ex-military bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.52,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.55,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two things in this world I can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:34.66,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}blintz: a thin pancake of Slavic origin, similar to a crêpe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.38,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold blintzes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:34.66,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,and idiotic ex-KGB shitheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.16,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Live with your head low so the bullets won't hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:52.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:04.31,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think kids nowadays would rather have \Nthose video games than these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:08.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think you'll have to endure this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.63,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the job of a vendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:16.06,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better than selling meth or women.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.58,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I do this because I want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,When the old man died, he left us this group that can barely get tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.15,0:16:34.43,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then only reason we've come this far is because the old man and the Kousa Council's last head took each other as brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:36.72,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they're gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:43.98,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,those bastards haven't let anyone take the head of our group, even after three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:47.67,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones left with any sense of obligation to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:52.48,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,He took care of me when I came from the Kyoto-Osaka district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:56.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:05.85,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin, you said that dealing with low-lives was a shame upon a yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that only matters if we have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.38,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.53,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pulling off a big job right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining up with the Russians to take out the guys above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.79,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They tried to take us out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:30.50,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Russians are Russians no matter where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:36.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have a shred of honor.\N So we need to take care of what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:41.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take it up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.72,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,that white scabbard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:49.49,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The name that still puts fear into all yakuza. \N"Man-slayer Ginji".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you show it to me once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:54.57,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:18:00.91,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful that you're looking after the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.12,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.37,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.92,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,what you're saying now doesn't have a shred of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:13.57,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I held the white scabbard for the old man, he had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.55,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Too bad, I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:21.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Russians,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.75,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,did they bring their own translator?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.73,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:33.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Young guy with a pretty but ill-bred looking girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.90,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he didn't look like anything more than a normal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.24,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to make an analogy,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:45.13,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,he looked like the guy who brings the bird, soup, onions, pot, and even the stove to a violent bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:49.04,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll be gone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.04,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.76,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for ya, but not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just until I finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I'm gone, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEngraver-Light\b1\fs23\be1\bord0\c&272E26&\frz-7\pos(349,258)}OKAJIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEngraver-Light\b1\fs23\be1\bord1\c&H98A295&\frz-7\pos(347,260)}OKAJIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:17.37,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky looks the same no matter where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:19.99,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here... at Mott Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.40,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:44.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.09,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.01,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Annie Oakley, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:50.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack McCall! I'm here to avenge Wild Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.08,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you defeat me, Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.32,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.78,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:10.56,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how people go down when they're shot.\NThey only go down like that in movies or TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:15.33,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, you suddenly lose all your strength. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:20.71,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like everything below your knees disappears, your feet stagger, and you go head first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.05,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:22.92,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:40.95,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not very cool looking, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.57,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like this when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.95,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's never that cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.72,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.20,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.25,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since about the time you charged into the Deadwood Saloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.54,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,The story is different than the one I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnEssai\fs25\fad(200,200)}"buy the farm": slang term meaning to die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.82,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calamity Jane didn't buy the farm in the saloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.30,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.96,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,My toy gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:05.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:11.51,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell Dutch or Benny about this, and I'll cut off your balls and pole and feed them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.06,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't! I won't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.19,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.35,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet your folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I went to their house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:24.53,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,but, I didn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.11,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:27.76,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.74,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.49,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still have a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.70,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:39.22,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:42.80,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like this place was made for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.32,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.97,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! The Russians aren't holding back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:22.88,Style1,,0000,0000,0000,,They blew something else up today!
